data.description: In the heart of downtown Cave Spring quaint Quail Ridge neighborhood, this newly remodeled 4 bedroom 3 bathroom home sits on the private back corner lot overlooking the gorgeous mountain range. The views from the rocking chair front porch make you feel like you are in a mountain villa while you are really close to the adorable historic downtown Cave Spring. This home has been newly remodeled with brand new LVP flooring, paint, new appliances, and so much more. The basement provides space for an extra bedroom with an attached full bathroom, or secondary entertaining space, office - or anything you can dream up. The tiled shower is stunning, the spacious walk in closets on main are boundless, and the open concept kitchen, dining and living room are perfect for entertaining. Don’t miss your chance to see this beautiful home for yourself!
